    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "Skill",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 1 poin <span style=\"color: #FF9999\">Pyro DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/16/25750596/1ce09211f025bf5470682189e0837732_650590365926932188.png",
                "id": "talent7287",
                "key": "Kaboom!",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Kaboom!"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 3 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro DMG</span>.<br>Karakter ini menerima status <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Explosive Spark</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Explosive Spark</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Saat Karakter yang terpengaruh melakukan Charged Att</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">ack:</span> Akan menghabiskan 1<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\"> Pyro</span> lebih sedikit dan DMG +1.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan: 1</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/18/25750596/ce0014e0d25cd397fef22aafb4b411c0_6247828819093643078.png",
                "id": "talent57112",
                "key": "Jumpy Dumpty",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Jumpy Dumpty"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 3 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro DMG</span> dan menciptakan <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Spark 'n' Splash</span> di area bermain lawan.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Spark 'n' Splash</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status Pertempuran</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Setelah Karaktermu menggunakan Skill</span>: Mengakibatkan 2 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro DMG</span> kepada Karakter Aktif di dalam tim.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan: 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/18/25750596/3f2b5db15d922d53d7d4db8261138f17_8034206171909971349.png",
                "id": "talent20911",
                "key": "Sparks 'n' Splash",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Sparks 'n' Splash"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Memberikan Pyro dan dapat memicu Reaksi Elemental berikut:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>]<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Melt</span>: DMG +2 poin untuk kasus ini</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>]<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Vaporize</span>: DMG +2 poin untuk kasus ini</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span>]<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Overloaded</span>: DMG +2 poin untuk kasus ini, target berganti ke Karakter selanjutnya secara paksa</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span>]<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, menciptakan [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning Flame</span>] yang mengakibatkan 1 poin Pyro DMG di akhir Ronde (Jumlah penggunaan sekali, maksimum 2 tumpukan)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/16/25750596/d714b3b669cc08d1d8e34464fd7a3630_5575431605663576658.png",
                "id": "talent71793",
                "key": "Pyro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Pyro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Charged Attack</span></strong></p><p>Jika total Dadu Elemental berjumlah genap sebelum Aksi Tempur giliranmu dimulai, maka Normal Attack yang digunakan akan dianggap sebagai Charged Attack.<br><br><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Penggunaan</span></strong></p><p>Setelah efek kartu ini dipicu, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan</span>-nya akan dikonsumsi.</p><p>Kartu ini akan langsung dibuang setelah semua <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan</span> telah dikonsumsi.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/03/04/25750596/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_283969296434866826.png",
                "id": "talent51736",
                "key": "Detail Peraturan",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Detail Peraturan"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
